{"tid":1379461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"義士線上心理輔導/樹洞","createTime":"2019-07-28T19:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T11:59:10.000Z","uid":50286,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c6b324e64893291d5f2f15790f12776814b5b692","tid":1379461,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:31:09.000Z","msg":"Hi 我係外國做開心理輔導既 係最近一次恐怖襲擊我都有輔導受害人，家屬同埋其他受到影響既人<br />\n<br />\n見到大家係香港博曬命我都想出一分力<br />\n<br />\n我唔識用tg所以開左個instagram比大家做樹洞或者約個時間一對一心理輔導（Skype, FaceTime) <br />\n<br />\n我同大家保證所有野係絕對保密 有需要既話可以叫我證明我係外國同埋我做開輔導個d野 如果冇你許可/consent所有野係絕對保密 絕對confidential<br />\n<br />\n我會盡量覆 或者如果巴絲打淨係想舒發下都可以係依個post到覆 <br />\n<br />\n如果你好急想要同人講野可以話我知 我會盡快覆你 因為都有時差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nInstagram: counsellinghk"},{"pid":"e4ce8945cedc918a8fa9d084e1141197781025ca","tid":1379461,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:36:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d462dea7a7dd8de4740527f38ecf76f92957bf14","tid":1379461,"uid":36742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:44:10.000Z","msg":"香港時間係5:43am<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會有啲揀錯時間開"},{"pid":"317862e6c6c2ef37c1a847eb74987356120a0cc5","tid":1379461,"uid":36742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:45:06.000Z","msg":"成個月訓唔撚到咁岩睇連登見到你個post都唔知講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ebba28a64dfb9b121c158b6fb052c1d47aa653","tid":1379461,"uid":229296,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d462dea7a7dd8de4740527f38ecf76f92957bf14","tid":1379461,"uid":36742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:44:10.000Z","msg":"香港時間係5:43am<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會有啲揀錯時間開"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T21:46:57.000Z","msg":"其實唔會，好多人訓唔著，佢地正需要樓主<br />\n同埋可以人手推返起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/